collections.description:
#Sad Guitar

This beautiful collection contains sad riffs played on electric guitar. In total there are 12 items 1/1.

#How was this collection made?

With the guitar plugged into the amp, I improvised approximately 50 riffs using the scales: Harmonic Minor, Aeolian and Ionic. Then I selected the 25 with good potential. So I did a second analysis and chose the 12 best riffs. After that, I recorded, mixed and mastered each one.

#Setup

- Guitar Amp
- Eletric Guitar
- Condenser Microphone
- Analog Overdrive Pedal
- Analog Compressor Pedal

#Quality

- .Wav 24-bit/48khz
- .PNG 3000 x 3000 px

#Music & Visuals

By Victor Ballogh
collections.name: Sad Guitar
